{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 75611, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学生开不开学和整体经济又没有太大关系，所以为什么要管你呢", "timestamp": 1593745907, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换个角度，这也是对学生负责啊，没必要说的这么难听吧，这就逃避责任了？", "timestamp": 1593745934, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75618, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "难道不应该这样？", "timestamp": 1593745973, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75641, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈哈哈哈哈，世一流", "timestamp": 1593746109, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75645, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 一刀切，懒政", "timestamp": 1593746122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "吓得我看了看北京这几天新增病例数，哦，一两个啊", "timestamp": 1593746127, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75656, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz说的其实是实话", "timestamp": 1593746175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果学校里出了一个那怎么办。", "timestamp": 1593746351, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75696, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果疫情严重不返校还说得过去，现在疫情控制住了还不返校就tm是懒政。中小学都开课这么久了。", "timestamp": 1593746582, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75708, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "回了学校又会有各种限制措施。到那个时候该不会又要骂学校吧。", "timestamp": 1593746833, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "北京现在的确实没办法回去啊，控制住了肯定能回去的", "timestamp": 1593747068, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75791, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要只站在自己的立场考虑问题", "timestamp": 1593747722, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 75929, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不给返校不正是学校在履行保障学生安全的责任吗？说的好像一句“领导逃避责任”能解释一切问题一样....", "timestamp": 1593749340, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 76075, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是我感染了新冠的话，对我的影响确实没有对领导的影响大呢。", "timestamp": 1593751238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 76080, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "北京很难啊，其他地区早就控制地妥妥的，不也没返校么。", "timestamp": 1593751260, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 76132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "额大家都觉得返校没有风险吗。首先清华校园大人多人杂，你可以控制住学生，但控制不住食堂阿姨打印店大叔后勤人员其他校内住的人。其次在学校大家每天换着波的亲密接触，食堂教室宿舍哪个不是高风险地区，一人感染全校玩完不是开玩笑的。", "timestamp": 1593752020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 76173, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 12989, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 至少我的高中朋友都返校了", "timestamp": 1593752656, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 12989, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "领导的乌纱帽，肯定比学生的利益重要啊。\n如果学习里出一个新发地那样的事，这些领导就都凉了。\n所以为了逃避责任，就都不返校呗。\n学生是最好欺负的罢了。", "timestamp": 1593745802, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782587, "url": "", "vote": {}}}